          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "College infrastructure is not big as compare to other colleges",
          "name": "Shashank Siwal",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "The staff are not so cooperative. If you've anh problem they'll make you wait for a long period of time to solve a minor 5 min problem.",
